Ports: Jiddah, Ad Dammam, Ras Tanura, Jizan, Al Jubayl, Yanbu al
Bahr, Yanbu al Sinaiyah
 
Merchant marine: 94 ships (1,000 GRT or over) totaling 1,988,322
